    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an action, you can target one creature within 60 feet of you that you can see to brand it with your draconic element. The target must succeed on a CHA save against your spell save DC or become vulnerable to the damage type associated with your draconic ancestry until the end of your next turn. A target resistant to that damage type loses that resistance for the duration, but a target immune to the damage type is still immune to it, even if the target fails the save.</p><p>Once used, you can't use this feature again until you finish a long rest, unless you spend 4 sorcery points to do so.</p>",
